headline: ADM to Present at 2025 Barclays Annual Global Consumer Staples Conference
summary: CHICAGO, August 13, 2025--ADM (NYSE: ADM) will present at the 2025 Barclays Annual Global Consumer Staples Conference on Wednesday, Sept. 3, in Boston. The company will participate in a fireside chat at 1:30 p.m. Eastern Time.
